      ],
      "table_notes": [
        "(1) CFF = 7% of Gross Sales. Gross Sales includes all services and installation, Core and Non-Core. Excludes Product sales and sales tax.",
        "(2) $2,500/month additional local marketing required for length of contract.",
        "(3) RMM agents based on volume; must be purchased from franchisor. Min 3 agents in Business.",
        "(8) Conversion franchise CFF waived on average existing Gross Sales for first 12 months.",
        "(9) Software/tech fees subject to change; portion payable to franchisor.",
        "(10) Local marketing includes LoyaltyLoop."
      ],
      "provenance": "Item 6, pages 11-14 of PDF"
